---
import Terminal from '../layouts/Terminal.astro';
---

<Terminal title="~/about_me">
	<div class="about">
		<p class="label">> cat /etc/about_me</p>

		<div class="block">
			<p>23, Australian American. General IT person. Jack of all trades, master of none, and honestly that has been useful for me.</p>
			<p class="deep-link"><a href="/who_am_i">[READ_FULL_BIOGRAPHY: ./who_am_i]</a></p>
		</div>

		<div class="block">
			<p class="label">> BACKGROUND:</p>
			<p>I've worn a lot of hats in my time, really. Network engineering, systems work, desktop support, Discord bot development. I was once "supposed" to be a backend dev or sysadmin, but life made me use JavaScript and do front end one too many times and now I can reasonably be described as a full stack dev. That's just how the cookie crumbles I suppose.</p>
			<p>I treat programming languages as different syntax over similar paradigms. If you understand the idea and read the docs, you can build in whatever language you need. Learn Haskell, learn C#, Python, and maybe some basics of C and you're basically set up to program however you wish.</p>
			<p>I'm also oddly interested in getting accessibility working, tab orders, all that kind of stuff.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="block">
			<p class="label">> INTERESTS:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Amateur meteorology</li>
				<li>Anime & manga</li>
				<li>Logical, efficient solutions to everything</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="block">
			<p class="label">> PROJECTS:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><span class="highlight">silky.moe</span>: this site</li>
				<li><span class="highlight">CeciliaBot</span>: local LLM connected to Discord with limited memory</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="block">
			<p class="label">> CONTACT:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="https://github.com/Silky777" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub: Silky777</a></li>
				<li>Discord: silkyren</li>
				<li>Fluxer: silkyren#0197</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="block">
			<p class="label">> PGP FINGERPRINT:</p>
			<p class="fingerprint">968F 9FE9 CA23 9F0B 3E0E  4F5D C4E8 8EF0 AACB BFDB</p>
			<p class="dim">↳ <a href="/pgp_public.asc" target="_blank">export public_key.asc</a></p>
		</div>

		<p class="prompt">guest@sys:~$ <span class="blink">_</span></p>
	</div>
</Terminal>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.block {
		border-left: 2px solid var(--phosphor);
		padding-left: 1rem;
	}

	.label {
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
		opacity: 0.7;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.dim {
		color: var(--phosphor-dim);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
	}

	li::before {
		content: "├─ ";
		opacity: 0.4;
	}

	li:last-child::before {
		content: "└─ ";
		opacity: 0.4;
	}

	.highlight {
		color: var(--phosphor);
		text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--phosphor);
	}

	.fingerprint {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	a {
		color: var(--phosphor);
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--phosphor);
	}

	a:hover {
		background: var(--phosphor);
		color: var(--bg-color);
		text-shadow: none;
	}

	a:focus,
	a:focus-visible {
		background: var(--phosphor);
		color: var(--bg-color);
		text-shadow: none;
		outline: 2px solid var(--phosphor);
		outline-offset: 2px;
	}

	.prompt {
		margin-top: 1rem;
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.blink {
		animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
	}

	@keyframes blink {
		50% { opacity: 0; }
	}
</style>
